      "concept.svg": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 720 340\" font-family=\"ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif\">\n  <style>\n    .box   { fill: #fef3c7; stroke: #92400e; stroke-width: 2; }\n    .ok    { fill: #dcfce7; stroke: #166534; stroke-width: 2; }\n    .arrow { stroke: #374151; stroke-width: 1.8; fill: none; marker-end: url(#a); }\n    .label { font-size: 13px; fill: #111827; }\n    .sub   { font-size: 11px; fill: #374151; }\n    .title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; fill: #111827; }\n    .axis  { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; fill: #6b7280; letter-spacing: .05em; }\n    .mono  { font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: 11px; fill: #1e3a8a; }\n  </style>\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"a\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"7\" markerHeight=\"7\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z\" fill=\"#374151\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"26\" class=\"title\">Closure traits — which one do you need?</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"60\" width=\"640\" height=\"36\" rx=\"6\" class=\"ok\"/>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"82\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">Fn  ⊂  FnMut  ⊂  FnOnce   (every Fn is an FnMut, every FnMut is an FnOnce)</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"40\"  y=\"120\" width=\"200\" height=\"160\" rx=\"8\" class=\"ok\"/>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"144\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">Fn</text>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"162\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">only reads captures</text>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"mono\">fn m(&amp;self, ...)</text>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">callable many times</text>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"218\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">shareable across threads*</text>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">example:</text>\n  <text x=\"140\" y=\"258\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"mono\">|x| x + 1</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"260\" y=\"120\" width=\"200\" height=\"160\" rx=\"8\" class=\"box\"/>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"144\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">FnMut</text>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"162\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">mutates captures</text>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"mono\">fn m(&amp;mut self, ...)</text>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">callable many times</text>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"218\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">exclusive access each call</text>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">example:</text>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"258\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"mono\">|x| { *count += 1; x }</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"480\" y=\"120\" width=\"200\" height=\"160\" rx=\"8\" class=\"box\"/>\n  <text x=\"580\" y=\"144\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">FnOnce</text>\n  <text x=\"580\" y=\"162\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">consumes captures</text>\n  <text x=\"580\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"mono\">fn m(self, ...)</text>\n  <text x=\"580\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">callable exactly once</text>\n  <text x=\"580\" y=\"218\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">moves the closure's data</text>\n  <text x=\"580\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"sub\">example:</text>\n  <text x=\"580\" y=\"258\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"mono\">move || drop(buf)</text>\n\n  <text x=\"40\" y=\"315\" class=\"sub\">Choose the loosest bound the callsite can live with. Fn &lt; FnMut &lt; FnOnce — every caller is happier with Fn.</text>\n  <text x=\"40\" y=\"330\" class=\"sub\">* Fn + Send + Sync to actually share across threads.</text>\n</svg>\n"
